description: Data file created by Yahoo! Messenger, an instant messaging application developed by Yahoo!; used by older versions of Yahoo! Messenger.

content: Yahoo Messenger! is used to send messages back and forth over the Internet. It is similar to Microsoft Windows Live Messenger (WLM) and AOL Instant Messenger.
